            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Bandai 最新推出的 METAL BUILD 系列龍王丸，可説是喚醒了許多 80 後玩家的童年回憶，《魔神英雄傳》一向也是小編的童年至愛動畫，這部龍神丸復活後的龍王丸，戰力大提升亦可以變形鳳王形態，Bandai 今次不僅在 METAL BUILD 龍王丸高度還原後，更加入了一些創新設計，可説是 METAL BUILD 系列的一大突破。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258413" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0422-452x580.jpg" alt="" width="452" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0422-452x580.jpg 452w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0422-scaled.jpg 701w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 452px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0423-465x580.jpg" alt="" width="465" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0423-465x580.jpg 465w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0423-scaled.jpg 722w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 465px" /></p><p>龍王丸本體高約 16cm，橫向寬度較大，整體存在感強。重量達 660g，拿在手中頗有份量。塗裝方面，電鍍金特別出色，天線和肩甲龍紋處呈現出純淨的黃金色澤，燈光照射下極為華麗。值得一提的是，肩甲背面還創新加入了鳳凰圖案，與前面的龍紋相映成趣；不過頭部黑色部份內藏的金龍頭，要用強光照射下才可隱約看到，一般的光源只是黑色的一大片，會比較單調。</p><p><a title="_DSC0425" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53941535427/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53941535427_8d6043b4a3_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0425" width="868" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0427" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942686248/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942686248_36b2d7ca90_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0427" width="1022" height="1024" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0820-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0820-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0820-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0429-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0429-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0429-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258429" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0430-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0430-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0430-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0433-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0433-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0433-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0434-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0434-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0434-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0435-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0435-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0435-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0436-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0436-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0436-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0438-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0438-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0438-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>配件方面，除了一把劍和一面盾牌外，還附帶兩個替換手型。劍可收納於盾中，盾牌的 4 片金色羽翼有展開功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0446-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0446-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0446-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0447-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0447-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0447-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258438" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0448-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0448-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0448-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258439" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0449-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0449-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0449-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0450-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0450-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0450-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>頭部、肩部、手肘等關節均有不同程度的可動，其中肩部採用二段式關節，內段還使用了齒輪結構，手感不錯。腿部關節同樣出色，屈膝時膝蓋裝甲還會聯動，細節豐富，不過腳腕的可動性較差，貼地性麻麻地。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0442-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0442-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0442-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0439-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0439-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0439-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0440-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0440-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0440-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0441-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0441-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0441-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>作為 METAL BUILD 系列首款可變形產品，龍王丸的變形結構可以用精妙來形容。從人形到鳳王形態的變形過程，基本還原原作設定，同時加入了很多的心思設計，例如多個連動位置，胸甲、鎖鏈發射器等部位的連動，以及拉出鳳王頭後，眼神的連動變換。變形後的鳳王形態造型優美，但需要支架輪助才可擺設，值得一讚的是，支架接口採用金屬材質，大大提升了承重能力和耐用性，之後的 METAL BUILD 的支架都是如此就好了。另外還具備「超鳳王」的二段變形，通過展開翅膀、調整尾部等變化，可呈現出更有霸氣的姿態，提升了可玩性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0818-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0818-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0818-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258450" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0819-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0819-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0819-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0488" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942437546/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942437546_f1bcf12ff1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0488" width="1024" height="761" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0496" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942770509/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942770509_99718a99ef_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0496" width="1024" height="758" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0498" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942770669/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942770669_ea0f24ae5d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0498" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0451-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0451-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0451-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0452-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0452-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0452-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0457" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942770534/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942770534_3d00214d76_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0457" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0462" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942893185/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942893185_817813dd28_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0462" width="1024" height="919" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0479" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53941535342/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53941535342_9d6629f617_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0479" width="917" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0484" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942686083/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942686083_4de12b9e33_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0484" width="1024" height="824" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>METAL BUILD 龍王丸無論在塗裝品質、把玩體驗還是創新設計上，都非常有水準。對於童年回憶的玩家而言，就好像小編那樣，其出色的做工和豐富的玩法，實在是非常吸引。</p><p><strong>METAL BUILD DRAGON SCALE 龍王丸</strong><br />
售價：33,000 日圓（含税）<br />
查詢：瑞華行</p><p><a title="_DSC0453" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53942686203/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53942686203_98d561dc4e_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0453" width="1024" height="720" /></a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/24/metal-build-ryuoumaru/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【評測】METAL BUILD 龍王丸　超鳳王二段變形</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
